data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your DREAM home! This meticulously crafted 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, featuring high ceilings and a cozy family room ideal for creating lasting memories. With a PRIVATE POOL on an OVERSIZED LOT this home is  newly renovated and move-in ready! Situated on a quiet street in the sought-after Breckenridge neighborhood in the beautiful Lake Toho area, this lovely home will certainly delight the new homeowner. The high ceilings create a sense of spaciousness and openness, providing a modern and elegant atmosphere throughout the home. The family room is the heart of the home, offering a warm and inviting space for relaxation, entertainment, and quality time with loved ones. Many important features and upgrades of this home include ROOF 2020 and ALL NEW double-paned windows in 2022. This property has a soft spot for the eyes with fresh interior and exterior paint, and Vinyl Flooring throughout the entirety of the home. Kitchen comes equipped with Granite CounterTops, Stainless Steel Appliances and Solid Wood Cabinets. The Master Bedroom features Double Walk-In Closets and an extraordinary ensuite bathroom with a seamless walk-in shower, a new vanity with dual sinks, granite countertops, and all new fixtures. Step outside to a well-maintained yard with your very own private pool, perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. With a highly desired floor plan, fresh upgrades, oversized lot, in a community with a Low HOA, this is the perfect property to call home to start the new year! Located near major highways, shopping plazas, Disney World, Lake Nona, and the International Airport. Come view this home today!
